race.comment: LADY NESS (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (37.55) last time in a R/A FIN at Sale. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. PAW HELION (6) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when third (42.54) at Sandown. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Hard to beat again. ARCHER SWEET (1) ran good time (42.55) when third last start over 715m at Sandown, the second placing in a row. Rates a winning chance on best. LADY BREANNA (7) has strong credentials over this journey.
